  "short_description": "OS OMEGA is an isometric twin-stick shooter / RPG game set in a retro synth wave environment. Fight gazillions of unique 3D enemies, use fully physical guns to defeat the V.I.R.U.S. and save the operating system. Novel tactics reward dancing around enemies and smart consumable management.",
